WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 24=

00:00:16.420 --> 00:00:18.660
Your touch is still the best.

00:00:19.220 --> 00:00:22.460
All these years, if not for you,

00:00:22.740 --> 00:00:24.700
I would've gone mad long ago.

00:00:25.940 --> 00:00:26.939
Your Highness,

00:00:26.940 --> 00:00:30.260
you've suffered all these years.

00:00:30.580 --> 00:00:32.500
Ugh.

00:00:34.020 --> 00:00:34.539
Filthy things.

00:00:34.540 --> 00:00:35.900
Just looking at them hurts the eyes.

00:00:36.540 --> 00:00:38.020
As long as your ears still work.

00:00:50.620 --> 00:00:52.379
You've worked hard too,

00:00:52.380 --> 00:00:54.660
helping me scheme all these years.

00:00:54.780 --> 00:00:56.100
Otherwise,

00:00:56.340 --> 00:00:59.860
that wretched Empress would've
trampled all over me long ago.

00:01:00.340 --> 00:01:02.060
Rest assured, Your Highness.

00:01:03.060 --> 00:01:05.260
Now that
the fate-swapping plan is complete,

00:01:06.340 --> 00:01:07.500
the world

00:01:07.980 --> 00:01:09.660
will still belong to you

00:01:10.140 --> 00:01:12.180
and the Crown Prince.

00:01:13.340 --> 00:01:15.260
You always say we're almost there.

00:01:15.340 --> 00:01:16.779
Exactly how much longer will it take?

00:01:16.780 --> 00:01:18.979
Hahaha!

00:01:18.980 --> 00:01:22.580
This time, we're truly only
one step away.

00:01:24.740 --> 00:01:26.019
Originally,

00:01:26.020 --> 00:01:28.940
there was something I could never
figure out all these years.

00:01:29.460 --> 00:01:31.340
Back then, I clearly cast a spell

00:01:31.540 --> 00:01:33.460
to ruin Xiao Heng's fate in marriage

00:01:33.540 --> 00:01:37.100
and make her reincarnate
into Xiao Jing's bloodline.

00:01:37.820 --> 00:01:40.539
Your Highness, do you know why

00:01:40.540 --> 00:01:44.379
Xiao Jing has remained
overlooked all these years?

00:01:44.380 --> 00:01:47.500
Even Xiao Rui is mediocre at best.

00:01:48.740 --> 00:01:49.860
Why is that?

00:01:51.020 --> 00:01:54.539
Because that abandoned girl,

00:01:54.540 --> 00:01:55.980
Suisui,

00:01:56.940 --> 00:01:59.540
was the lucky star from back then.

00:02:11.540 --> 00:02:14.860
Xiao Jing mistook the lucky star
for a jinx and abandoned her,

00:02:16.220 --> 00:02:18.060
but Xiao Heng picked her up instead.

00:02:18.740 --> 00:02:21.540
In the end,
it was Xiao Heng who benefited.

00:02:27.340 --> 00:02:29.180
But don't worry, Your Highness.

00:02:29.580 --> 00:02:32.299
Once I sacrifice her,

00:02:32.300 --> 00:02:33.820
then her fortune

00:02:33.860 --> 00:02:35.700
will belong

00:02:35.740 --> 00:02:38.380
to Your Highness, won't it?

00:02:39.780 --> 00:02:41.460
Good.

00:02:42.260 --> 00:02:45.820
Looks like you really
were meant to be my daughter.

00:02:46.540 --> 00:02:47.779
That's what I thought.

00:02:47.780 --> 00:02:49.659
I'm so lovable

00:02:49.660 --> 00:02:50.779
and adored by everyone.

00:02:50.780 --> 00:02:53.380
How could I possibly
have such an ugly father?

00:02:54.540 --> 00:02:56.339
Father, now that you mention it,

00:02:56.340 --> 00:03:01.340
we do make a good-looking
father and daughter pair.

00:03:01.860 --> 00:03:02.980
Your Highness,

00:03:04.300 --> 00:03:05.980
there's still something

00:03:06.220 --> 00:03:08.060
I can't figure out.

00:03:08.540 --> 00:03:11.540
Please enlighten me, Your Highness.

00:03:12.020 --> 00:03:12.859
Mm.

00:03:12.860 --> 00:03:14.100
Go ahead.

00:03:15.660 --> 00:03:20.219
Xiao Heng and Xiao Jing
are both your sons.

00:03:20.220 --> 00:03:22.739
Are you truly willing
to sacrifice Xiao Heng

00:03:22.740 --> 00:03:24.500
to fulfill Xiao Jing?

00:03:29.340 --> 00:03:31.299
When did I ever say

00:03:31.300 --> 00:03:34.780
Xiao Heng was my biological son?

00:03:35.460 --> 00:03:36.419
(No way.)

00:03:36.420 --> 00:03:38.980
(How did this gossip
end up involving my father?)

00:03:39.860 --> 00:03:43.700
Back then, that wretched Empress
monopolized all the Emperor's favor.

00:03:43.820 --> 00:03:45.860
Not long after, she became pregnant.

00:03:46.420 --> 00:03:48.660
So I pretended to be pregnant too.

00:03:48.980 --> 00:03:52.180
I found a pregnant woman
outside the palace

00:03:52.500 --> 00:03:54.220
and hid her in a secret chamber,

00:03:54.900 --> 00:03:56.780
waiting for her to give birth.

00:03:57.820 --> 00:03:59.619
Who knew that woman's fate was so poor

00:03:59.620 --> 00:04:01.699
that she gave birth
to a stillborn child.

00:04:01.700 --> 00:04:03.579
Just as I was worrying
about how to explain it,

00:04:03.580 --> 00:04:07.380
that wretched Empress
went into labor at the same time.

00:04:24.580 --> 00:04:27.780
Even Heaven was helping me.

00:04:28.500 --> 00:04:32.740
I swapped the dead baby
for her newborn son

00:04:33.700 --> 00:04:35.300
and made her bear the blame

00:04:36.340 --> 00:04:40.420
for causing the prince's death.

00:04:40.900 --> 00:04:43.459
She couldn't defend herself

00:04:43.460 --> 00:04:45.180
and died in despair.

00:04:45.660 --> 00:04:49.620
Xiao Heng then became my son.

00:04:58.240 --> 00:05:01.559
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:05.399
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:05.400 --> 00:05:08.919
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:11.880
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:12.760 --> 00:05:16.399
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:20.160
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:23.559
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:27.600
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:33.200 --> 00:05:36.879
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:40.519
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:40.520 --> 00:05:44.239
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:47.879
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:51.559
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:53.479
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:05:53.480 --> 00:05:59.680
♪Good fortune♪